description:
The R script generates a probit model as an element of an experimental procedure to analyze the sensitivity of a quantitative real-time PCR method. The script outputs a text report of the run, plots of the model (PDF), and an Excel-compatible file with both the text and the graphic data. 

 &nbsp; 

 &nbsp;

